‚ô™ Nothing alive can see
the way you do ‚ô™

39:15.020 --> 39:16.087
Mom?

39:16.187 --> 39:17.823
My baby...

39:22.160 --> 39:23.995
We did it.

39:24.095 --> 39:25.764
The podcast helped.

39:25.864 --> 39:27.766
‚ô™ Time ‚ô™

39:29.200 --> 39:31.470
Oh, did you get the...?
Oh, yeah.

39:35.073 --> 39:37.609
Thank you.

39:47.453 --> 39:51.757
‚ô™ Time to feel ‚ô™

39:51.857 --> 39:55.293
‚ô™ The space in you ‚ô™

