‚ô™ Time... ‚ô™

39:58.897 --> 40:02.200
So, did you get
everything you need?

40:02.300 --> 40:03.535
I did. Yeah.

40:03.635 --> 40:05.604
I think this is
gonna be an amazing

40:05.704 --> 40:06.738
series of episodes.

40:06.838 --> 40:10.576
So, what about like,
another date?

40:10.676 --> 40:12.844
Sometime, you know,
without the furnace

40:12.944 --> 40:14.245
and someone
trying to kill us.

40:14.345 --> 40:15.847
You know,
I didn't really mind

40:15.947 --> 40:17.248
the danger part of it.

40:17.348 --> 40:18.884
Switching things up,

40:18.984 --> 40:20.085
fighting for our lives.

40:20.185 --> 40:21.753
Made for
pretty good material.

40:21.853 --> 40:23.655
Yeah.
Yeah.

40:23.755 --> 40:26.592
Yeah?
Yeah, let's,
let's do that date

40:26.692 --> 40:28.694
when I get back
from my next podcast

40:28.794 --> 40:30.395
in Portland.

40:30.496 --> 40:33.031
Maine.
Huh...

40:33.131 --> 40:36.001
But, uh...

40:36.968 --> 40:39.170
you want to keep this for me
till I get back?

40:39.270 --> 40:40.438
Your jimmy kit thing?

