Are you kidding me?

41:41.567 --> 41:44.703
I am so sorry I missed it.

41:45.704 --> 41:47.205
Okay, let's just cut the cake.

41:47.305 --> 41:48.774
Mom, wait. Listen.

41:48.874 --> 41:50.576
I...

41:50.576 --> 41:51.943
I didn't realize back then

41:52.043 --> 41:54.179
how important
